'''天主教南非軍中教長區'''（{{lang-la|Ordinariatus Militaris Africa Australis}}；{{lang-en|Military Ordinariate of South Africa}}）是[[南非|南非]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[軍中教長區|軍中教長區]]，直屬[[聖座|聖座]]。此軍中教長區負責牧養信奉天主教的南非軍人及其家眷。

1951年5月17日成立軍中代牧區，1986年7月21日升為軍中教長區<ref>{{cite web |author1=Ioannes Paulus PP. II |title=SPIRITUALI MILITUM CURAE |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19860421_spirituali-militum-curae.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-02-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223185011/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19860421_spirituali-militum-curae.html |archivedate=2020-02-23 |language=la |date=1986-04-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。軍中教長區於2003年時有一個堂區和三名司鐸。

教長一職由[[天主教比勒陀利亞總教區|比勒陀利亞總教區總主教]]兼任。現任軍中教長為{{link-en|達布拉·姆帕科|Dabula Mpako|達布拉·安多尼·姆帕科}}<ref name="Vatican20190430">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 30.04.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/04/30/190430a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809184616/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/04/30/190430a.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=en |date=2019-04-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休軍中教長為{{link-de|喬治·方濟各·丹尼爾|George Francis Daniel}}、{{link-de|保祿·曼德拉·庫馬洛|Paul Mandla Khumalo}}和{{link-de|威廉·斯拉特瑞|William Slattery|威廉·彌額爾·斯拉特瑞}}<ref name="Vatican20190430" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 24.11.2008 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/11/24/0731/01809.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809185752/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/11/24/0731/01809.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=it |date=2008-11-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 15.12.2009 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/12/15/0787/01867.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809190330/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/12/15/0787/01867.html |archivedate=2019-08-09 |language=it |date=2009-12-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

